text: Luciano Cozzi (9 September 1909 - 18 September 1996) was an Italian diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:1996 deaths Category:Italian male divers Category:Olympic divers of Italy Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Milan
